      <guid>http://localhost:1313/nginx-agent/configuration/health-checks/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 &#xA;id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview  &lt;a class=&#34;headerlink float-right&#34; href=&#34;#overview&#34; title=&#34;Overview&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link fa-xs&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The REST API includes a health endpoint to verify the status of NGINX Agent.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 &#xA;id=&#34;configure-the-rest-api&#34;&gt;Configure the REST API  &lt;a class=&#34;headerlink float-right&#34; href=&#34;#configure-the-rest-api&#34; title=&#34;Configure the REST API&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link fa-xs&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;To enable the REST API, add the following configuration to the NGINX Agent configuration file, &lt;code&gt;/etc/nginx-agent/nginx-agent.conf&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;code-block&#34; data-mf=&#34;true&#34; style=&#34;display: none;&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;code-type chroma&#34;&gt;nginx&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;code-container chroma&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;button onclick=&#34;copyToClipBoard(this, &amp;#34;id-18440f1e8f07be80&amp;#34;)&#34; class=&#34;code-copy-button multi-line&#34; type=&#34;button&#34;&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;highlight-v2&#34; id=&#34;id-18440f1e8f07be80&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-nginx&#34; data-lang=&#34;nginx&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;api:&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;host:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;127&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;.0.0.1&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;port:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34